incoming.page_description.text: Tohatoha mōhiohio hira mā te haumaru ki tō mātou rōpū tautoko

incoming.feature_disabled_description.text: Kua monokia tēnei āhuatanga i tēnei wā. Tēnā whakapā atu ki te tautoko mō te āwhina.

incoming.memo_placeholder.text: Whakamārama poto (hei tauira, Tono tautuhi anō kupuhipa)

incoming.memo_hint.text: Āwhinatia mātou ki te tuku tō karere ki te tangata tika

incoming.recipient_aria_label.text: Kōwhiria he kaiwhiwhi mō tēnei karere huna

incoming.recipient_hint.text: Kōwhiria ko wai hei whiwhi i tēnei karere haumaru

incoming.no_recipients_available.text: Kāore he kaiwhiwhi e wātea ana

incoming.secret_content_placeholder.text: Whakapiri mōhiohio hira ki konei (kupuhipa, kī, me ērā atu)

incoming.secret_content_hint.text: Ka whakamuhumuhu tēnei mōhiohio, kotahi noa te wā e taea ai te tiro

incoming.success_info_title.text: He aha te mea ka tū?

incoming.success_info_description.text: Ka taea e te kaiwhiwhi te tiro i tēnei karere huna kotahi noa te wā. Whai muri i tā rātou tirohanga, ka mukua pūmau te karere huna.

incoming.tagline1.text: Tohatoha mōhiohio hira mā te haumaru

incoming.tagline2.text: Pupuri i ngā kupuhipa me ngā raraunga tūmataiti kia kaua e puta i ngā pūrongo īmēra me te kōrerorero
